title: Expandable Bamboo Cutlery Drawer Organizer; bamboo organizer tray, expandable bamboo cutlery tray
description:
Conveniently organize your kitchen and desk drawers with this Seville Classics Expandable Drawer Organizer. 

Made of high quality bamboo and constructed with attractive, clean joints for added durability. Bamboo is 16 percent more durable than solid maple. 

Featuring five compartments, this ingeniously organizer expands smoothly in width to custom-fit in drawers and maximize storage space. 

This useful organizer is ideal for holding your flatware, cutlery, kitchen gadgets and clearing the clutter around the kitchen.
